title: Dell S2216H Unboxing | Hands On Review
description:
This is hands down one of the best budget 22 inch monitor. Being the latest one from the Dell S series lineup it replaces the popular Dell S2240L and adds many more features at almost the same price of around Rs.8000. 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Here's the link to purchase this monitor (India only) -
goo.gl/eW5NPC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Here are a few key specs for those who are interested-
1) 21.5 inch Full HD IPS 60Hz Panel
2) 2 x 3W integrated speakers
3) HDMI, VGA, Audio In and Audio Out ports
4) 6 ms gray to gray response time
5) Contrast Ratio 1000: 1, Dynamic Contrast Ratio : 8 Million: 1
